Definition: characterized by ascetic solitude
Example: the eremitic element in the life of a religious colony; his hermitic existence
Synonyms: noun, person, anchorite, eremitic, eremite, eremitical, hermitic, hermit, hermitical, characterized, by, ascetic, solitude, the, element, in, life, of, a, religious, colony, his, existence
Category: adj.all
